    "tag": "tscircuit/tscircuit.com#3461",
    "number": 3461,
    "title": "fix: preserve full redirect URL (path, query, and hash) on login and session timeout",
    "description": "Fixes the issue where logging back in after a session timeout discards the users location state, search parameters, or hash fragments, ensuring users are redirected back to their intended location with full URL structure preserved.",
    "contributor": "itisrohit",
    "repo": "tscircuit/tscircuit.com",
    "url": "https://github.com/tscircuit/tscircuit.com/pull/3461",
    "mostly_style": false,
    "new_page_or_component": false,
    "introduces_or_fixes_a_footprint": false,
    "core_change": true,
    "only_dependency_update": false,
    "bad_title": false,
    "introduces_new_circuit_board": false,
    "fixes_circuit_board": false,
    "fixes_subtle_important_bug": false,
    "minor_fix": false,
    "major_autorouter_bug_fix": false,
    "only_adds_autorouter_fixtures": false,
    "only_reproduces_a_bug": false,
    "reproduces_and_fixes_a_bug": false,
    "minor_developer_experience_improvement": false,
    "major_experience_improvement": true,
    "introduces_new_schematic_symbol": false,
    "fixes_schematic_representation": false,
    "improves_parts_engine": false,
    "add_design_to_schematic_corpus": false,
    "major_improvement_to_core_data_modeling": false,
    "major_library_algorithm_contribution": false,
    "substantially_improves_svg_generation": false,
    "user": {
      "login": "itisrohit"
    },
    "html_url": "https://github.com/tscircuit/tscircuit.com/pull/3461",
    "created_at": "2026-05-20T08:57:13Z",
    "merged_at": "2026-05-20T15:23:29Z",
    "body": "## Summary\n\nResolves the issue where logging back in after a session timeout (or direct access to protected paths) discards the user's location state, search parameters, or hash fragments (such as compressed playground code inside the `#data:` hash).\n\n### Key Improvements:\n1. **Dynamic Toast Location Capture**: Updated the session-expired toast handler in `src/hooks/use-axios.tsx` to read the location dynamically from the browser `window.location` at click-time. This eliminates the stale closure bug in the memoized toast block from past PRs (where `orgLoginRedirect` was stale when the user navigated).\n2. **Protected Settings Preservation**:\n   - `src/pages/package-settings.tsx` and `src/pages/user-settings.tsx` now preserve the full URL structure (`pathname + search + hash`) as a query parameter when bouncing unauthenticated users to `/login`.\n3. **Robust Google/OAuth Re-authentication**:\n   - Updated `src/pages/login.tsx` to extract the `redirect` query parameter and redirect the authenticated user back to their intended target.\n4. **Open-Redirect Protection**:\n   - Included a strict validation check (`redirectParam.startsWith(\"/\")`) to prevent open-redirect vulnerabilities, ensuring only local relative redirects are allowed.\n\nCloses #3023\n\n---\n\n## Test Plan / Walkthrough\n\n### 1. Session Expiry Flow (Editor / Playground)\n1. Log in to `tscircuit.com`.\n2. Open any package or snippet editor containing a hash code block:\n   `http://localhost:5173/editor?snippet_id=123#data:application/gzip;base64,...`\n3. Simulate a session timeout:\n   - Run in the browser console: `localStorage.clear()` (or clear cookies/session state).\n   - Trigger a backend request to get a `401 Unauthorized`.\n4. Click the **\"Session Expired. Click to login\"** toast that appears.\n5. Verify you are navigated to `/login?redirect=...`.\n6. Complete the login flow and verify you are redirected exactly back to the URL with the complete search query (`?snippet_id=123`) and hash fragment (`#data:...`) intact.\n\n### 2. Direct Settings Access\n1. Open an incognito browser window or log out.\n2. Direct-navigate to:\n   - `/settings`\n   - `/<author>/<packageName>/settings`\n3. Verify you are redirected to `/login?redirect=%2Fsettings` (or the respective package settings path).\n4. Log in and verify you are redirected back to the correct settings page.\n\n---\n\n## Demonstration Video\n\nHere is the recorded verification video demonstrating the session timeout bounce and direct settings redirects preserving full URL states (pathname, search query, and hash fragments):\n\nhttps://github.com/itisrohit/tscircuit.com/releases/download/v0.0.1-assets/session_timeout_redirect_verification.mov\n\n",
    "state": "merged",
    "isAlignedWithMilestone": false,
    "starRating": 3,
    "impact": "Major"
  },
